# Crypto Price Tracker

This is a simple web app that shows the current price of Bitcoin (BTC) in both USD and Nigerian Naira (NGN).  
It fetches live Bitcoin prices using the CoinDesk API and converts USD to NGN at a fixed exchange rate.

## Features
- Real-time Bitcoin price in USD
- Converted Bitcoin price in NGN (â‚¦)
- Updates every minute automatically

## How to Use
1. Open the `crypto_price_tracker.html` file in a web browser.
2. The Bitcoin price will load and update every 60 seconds.

## Technologies Used
- HTML
- JavaScript (Fetch API)

